---
/* About section component for Space for Neurodiversity */
---
<!-- About Section -->
<section id="about" class="about section">

  <!-- Section Title -->
  <div class="container section-title text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <div><span>Discover</span> <span class="description-title">Space for Neurodiversity</span></div>
  </div>
  <!-- End Section Title -->

  <div class="container">

    <div class="row gx-5 align-items-center">
      
      <!-- Image Column -->
      <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="about-image position-relative text-center text-lg-start">
          <img src="img/hero-sfn.png"
               class="img-fluid rounded-4 shadow-sm"
               alt="Space for Neurodiversity hero image"
               loading="lazy">
          <div class="experience-badge">
            <span class="years">10+</span>
            <span class="text">Years Advocating Inclusion</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content Column -->
      <div class="col-lg-6 mt-4 mt-lg-0" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="300">
        <div class="about-content">
          <h2>Advancing Neurodiversity Across the Space Sector</h2>
          <p>
            Space for Neurodiversity is a pioneering initiative promoting inclusion, representation, and meaningful participation of neurodivergent individuals in space-related fields. We partner with organisations, research institutions, and innovators to:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Create inclusive workplaces and practices for neurodivergent talent</li>
            <li>Deliver educational resources, guidance, and frameworks for equity</li>
            <li>Foster collaboration, awareness, and community engagement across the sector</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We believe lasting impact requires vision, advocacy, and actionable insight, and we bring all three to every project, partnership, and initiative.
          </p>

          <!-- Features -->
          <div class="row g-4 mt-3">

            <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="400">
              <div class="feature-item">
                <i class="bi bi-people-fill"></i>
                <h5>Inclusive Practices</h5>
                <p>
                  We provide guidance and support to ensure organisations adopt policies and practices that empower neurodivergent team members to thrive.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="450">
              <div class="feature-item">
                <i class="bi bi-lightbulb-fill"></i>
                <h5>Awareness & Advocacy</h5>
                <p>
                  Through research, workshops, and public initiatives, we raise awareness about neurodiversity and drive systemic change in the space industry.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>

          <a href="/get-involved" class="btn btn-primary mt-4">Get Involved</a>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>
<!-- /About Section -->